<div class="introduction-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				
				<div class="col-sm-12">
                <!--<img src="images/media_img.jpg" alt="" class="pull-right mr_l" width="432" />-->
					
					<div class="introduction-text">
						<p>Pioneer of the concept of Citizen Journalism in India, www.merinews.com is an award winning, India’s largest and the oldest citizen journalism based news portal. It is also featured amongst the top citizen journalism portals of the world. </p>
                        <p>Winner of India's BEST e-CONTENT AWARD , Official Honoree at Webby Awards, alongside the likes of <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/asia" target="_blank">Bloomberg.com</a> & <a href="http://www.aol.com/news/" target="_blank">aolnews.com</a>, <a href="http://edition.cnn.com/" target="_blank">cnn.com</a>. – <a href="http://www.merinews.com/" target="_blank">merinews.com</a> is powered by over 70,000 Citizen Journalists.</p>
                        <p>"Citizen Journalism" or Participatory Journalism is an evolving form of journalism through user generated news content. When any common man in his capacity as a citizen of a nation takes up the initiative to report things or express his views about happenings around him then the occurrence is popularly termed as citizen journalism or participatory journalism.</p>
                        <p>merinews&reg; through the concept of Citizen Journalism and  is building online platform which is breaking free from the conventional media bias at the same time takes the local news to a global platform where NEWS is BY THE PEOPLE, Of THE PEOPLE for THE PEOPLE. </p>
                        <p>News content &copy;merinews.com is often referred as a source by global media players like Daily News, National Geographic, CNN-IBN, NDTV, HT Media to name a few. </p>
                        <p>www.merinews.com is owned and promoted by Bizsol Advisors Pvt. Ltd. – an IAP Group Company.</p>
                        <p>merinews&reg; is a registered trade mark of Bizsol Advisors Pvt. Ltd. </p>
                        <p>For further details please visit <strong><a href="http://www.merinews.com/" target="_blank">www.merinews.com</a></strong></p>
					</div>
					
                    
